--*.comment: should be ignored due to having complex syntax

-ms-scrollbar-3dlight-color.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

font-family.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

display.comment: should be ignored due to varying semantics based on element

all.comment: should be ignored for having no practical initial value

-webkit-appearance.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

-webkit-appearance-std-dummy.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

color.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

outline-color.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

text-align.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

text-size-adjust.comment: should be ignored due to being user agent dependent

border-block-end.comment: should be ignored due to having complex syntax (multiple initial)

box-align.comment: should be ignored due to being unpredictable / nonstandard

animation-delay.comment: should be included in fromInitial: '0s' is shorter

mask-border-mode.comment: should be included in fromInitial: 'alpha' is shorter

mix-blend-mode.comment: should be included in fromInitial: 'normal' is shorter

offset-position.comment: should be included in fromInitial: 'auto' is shorter

block-overflow.comment: should be included in fromInitial: 'clip' is shorter

background-clip.comment: should be included in toInitial: 'border-box' is longer

background-size.comment: should be included in toInitial: 'auto auto' is longer

transform-origin.comment: should be included in toInitial: '50% 50% 0' is longer

border-image-repeat.comment: should be ignored since 'stretch' is same length as 'initial' (nothing to gain)

color-adjust.comment: should be ignored since 'economy' is same length as 'initial' (nothing to gain)
